If you are not satisfied with your purchase you can return the item for free for a full refund by the same payment method we received your payment.
The product must be intact, with all stickers, tags in place with original packaging and must not show any signs of use.
Ask for a Return Material Authorization and you will receive our confirmation plus a Label to attach in the package and drop off at any UPS location.
